{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "my-bank-collection-001",
    "name": "MY-Bank Platform",
    "description": "Core Banking Simulator + Bank User Service + Keycloak auth + WSO2 APIM gateway.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman.\n2. Open collection **Variables** and set `admin_password`.\n3. Run **Keycloak → Get Access Token** or **API Gateway → Login via Gateway**.\n4. Then run Bank User, Core Banking, or API Gateway requests.\n\n## URLs\n- Gateway: https://api.dental-care.me (or https://localhost:8243 local)\n- Auth: https://auth.dental-care.me\n- Core: https://core-api.dental-care.me\n- Users: https://users-api.dental-care.me",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "auth_base_url",
      "value": "https://auth.dental-care.me"
    },
    {
      "key": "core_base_url",
      "value": "https://core-api.dental-care.me"
    },
    {
      "key": "users_base_url",
      "value": "https://users-api.dental-care.me"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_gateway_base_url",
      "value": "https://localhost:8243"
    },
    {
      "key": "api_gateway_local_url",
      "value": "https://localhost:8243"
    },
    {
      "key": "keycloak_realm",
      "value": "bank"
    },
    {
      "key": "keycloak_client_id",
      "value": "bank-web"
    },
    {
      "key": "admin_username",
      "value": "admin"
    },
    {
      "key": "admin_password",
      "value": "CHANGE_ME"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "keycloak_client_secret",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Leave empty for public client bank-web. Required if client authentication is ON."
    },
    {
      "key": "staff_user_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "cif",
      "value": "CIF10001"
    },
    {
      "key": "account_number",
      "value": "ACC-10001-01"
    },
    {
      "key": "from_account",
      "value": "ACC-10001-02"
    },
    {
      "key": "to_account",
      "value": "ACC-10001-01"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Keycloak (Login / Logout / Refresh)",
      "description": "Auth is handled by Keycloak, NOT bank-user service.\nbank-user only validates JWT on /bank-users routes.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login - Get Access Token (password grant)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', data.access_token);",
                  "    if (data.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', data.refresh_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Token received', () => pm.expect(data.access_token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "} else {",
                  "    pm.test('Token request failed', () => pm.expect.fail(pm.response.text()));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "password"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "{{keycloak_client_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "username",
                  "value": "{{admin_username}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "password",
                  "value": "{{admin_password}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_secret",
                  "value": "{{keycloak_client_secret}}",
                  "description": "Only if bank-web is confidential",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{auth_base_url}}/realms/{{keycloak_realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token",
              "host": ["{{auth_base_url}}"],
              "path": [
                "realms",
                "{{keycloak_realm}}",
                "protocol",
                "openid-connect",
                "token"
              ]
            },
            "description": "Login via Keycloak (OIDC token endpoint).\n\nFix unauthorized_client:\n1. Realm must be `bank`\n2. Client `bank-web` must exist in bank realm\n3. Direct access grants = ON\n4. If Client authentication = OFF (public): do NOT send client_secret\n5. If Client authentication = ON: enable client_secret body field above"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', data.access_token);",
                  "    if (data.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', data.refresh_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "grant_type",
                  "value": "refresh_token"
                },
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "{{keycloak_client_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "refresh_token",
                  "value": "{{refresh_token}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{auth_base_url}}/realms/{{keycloak_realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/token"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "client_id",
                  "value": "{{keycloak_client_id}}"
                },
                {
                  "key": "refresh_token",
                  "value": "{{refresh_token}}"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": "{{auth_base_url}}/realms/{{keycloak_realm}}/protocol/openid-connect/logout",
            "description": "Ends Keycloak session and invalidates refresh token."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "OpenID Configuration (discovery)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{auth_base_url}}/realms/{{keycloak_realm}}/.well-known/openid-configuration",
            "description": "Lists all OIDC endpoints (token, logout, jwks, etc.)"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Core Banking",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Seed Demo Data",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/seed",
            "description": "Reset and load demo CIF10001 / CIF10002 data. Run once before other core tests."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Customer by CIF",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/customers/{{cif}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Customer Accounts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/customers/{{cif}}/accounts"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Account",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/accounts/{{account_number}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Account Transactions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{core_base_url}}/core/accounts/{{account_number}}/transactions?limit=20",
              "host": ["{{core_base_url}}"],
              "path": ["core", "accounts", "{{account_number}}", "transactions"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "limit",
                  "value": "20"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Account Holds",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/accounts/{{account_number}}/holds"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Place Hold",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"amount\": \"100.00\",\n  \"reason\": \"MANUAL\",\n  \"reference\": \"postman-hold-1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/accounts/{{account_number}}/holds"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Internal Transfer",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{access_token}}"
              },
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"from_account\": \"{{from_account}}\",\n  \"to_account\": \"{{to_account}}\",\n  \"amount\": \"500.00\",\n  \"idempotency_key\": \"postman-transfer-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"simulate\": \"success\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{core_base_url}}/core/transfers/internal"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Bank User - Auth (via service)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', data.access_token);",
                  "    if (data.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', data.refresh_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{admin_username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{admin_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/auth/login",
            "description": "Login via bank-user BFF → Keycloak. No direct Keycloak URL needed."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', data.access_token);",
                  "    if (data.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', data.refresh_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/auth/refresh"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh_token\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/auth/logout"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "API Gateway (WSO2)",
      "description": "Requests via WSO2 APIM. Run Keycloak login first for authenticated calls.\nLocal: api_gateway_base_url=https://localhost:8243\nRemote: https://api.dental-care.me",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Core Health (gateway)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_gateway_base_url}}/core-banking/1.0.0/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Bank User Health (gateway)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_gateway_base_url}}/bank-user/1.0.0/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login via Gateway",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', data.access_token);",
                  "    if (data.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', data.refresh_token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{admin_username}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{admin_password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{api_gateway_base_url}}/bank-user/1.0.0/auth/login"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Customer via Gateway",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{access_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_gateway_base_url}}/core-banking/1.0.0/core/customers/{{cif}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Staff via Gateway",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{access_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{api_gateway_base_url}}/bank-user/1.0.0/bank-users?status=active"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Internal Transfer via Gateway",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "bearer",
              "bearer": [
                {
                  "key": "token",
                  "value": "{{access_token}}",
                  "type": "string"
                }
              ]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"from_account\": \"{{from_account}}\",\n  \"to_account\": \"{{to_account}}\",\n  \"amount\": \"500.00\",\n  \"idempotency_key\": \"gw-transfer-{{$timestamp}}\",\n  \"simulate\": \"success\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{api_gateway_base_url}}/core-banking/1.0.0/core/transfers/internal"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Bank User (Staff)",
      "auth": {
        "type": "bearer",
        "bearer": [
          {
            "key": "token",
            "value": "{{access_token}}",
            "type": "string"
          }
        ]
      },
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/health"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Staff User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const data = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('staff_user_id', data.id);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"ali.retail\",\n  \"email\": \"ali.retail@bank.example\",\n  \"full_name\": \"Ali Retail\",\n  \"role\": \"retail\",\n  \"department\": \"Operations\",\n  \"temporary_password\": \"TempPass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/bank-users",
            "description": "Requires admin or supervisor role. Creates user in Keycloak + DB. Role must be: admin, supervisor, or retail."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Staff Users",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{users_base_url}}/bank-users?status=active",
              "host": ["{{users_base_url}}"],
              "path": ["bank-users"],
              "query": [
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "active"
                },
                {
                  "key": "role",
                  "value": "retail",
                  "disabled": true
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Staff User by ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/bank-users/{{staff_user_id}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Staff Role",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"role\": \"bank_auditor\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/bank-users/{{staff_user_id}}/role"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Disable Staff User",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"disabled\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/bank-users/{{staff_user_id}}/status"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Staff User",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{users_base_url}}/bank-users/{{staff_user_id}}",
            "description": "Requires admin role only."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
